    "body": "Fixes #7516. (I'm reluctant to fix it just for guarranteed destruction order, because I think that's a bit dangerous to promise, but I think the change is an overall improvement anyway).\r\n\r\nInstead store the relevant data directly, which should hopefully improve things by giving slightly more direct access. I also spotted that the `self` attribute of CyFunctions was never changed and so we can reliably assume its value in most cases.",
